node.text:
Japan’s fashion scene is on a different level 😮‍💨

The creativity, the silhouettes, the attention to detail, you can really feel it when you walk into these stores. A lot of the brands focus heavily on quality and fabric, but the prices are still surprisingly reasonable for what you’re getting.

If Japan is on your travel list, 💾 save this for later!

These are just my top 5, I mapped out 52 stores in total and will continue to add more.

Comment “TOKYO” and I’ll send you the full Google Maps list!

Happy shopping :)
